" காட்டுகிறது:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:458
#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:566
#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:738
msgid ""
