#: ../../docs/user_manual/working_with_vector/vector_properties.rst:1408
msgid ""
"At the top of the dialog, a :guilabel:`Value` drop-down list is enabled. You"
" can select an attribute column to use for labeling. By default, the "
":ref:`display field <maptips>` is used. Click |expression| if you want to "
